OL,5, Police officers are switching off their
OL,6, body-worn cameras when force is used,  
OL,7, as well as deleting footage and sharing
OL,8, videos on WhatsApp.                    
OL,10,FA BBC investigation has uncovered more 
OL,11,Fthan 150 reports of camera misuse by   
OL,12,Fforces in England and Wales - described
OL,13,Fas "shocking" by a leading officer.    
OL,15,FIn one case, siblings faced a two-year 
OL,16,Flegal battle over footage showing      
OL,17,Fofficers' use of force against them.   
OL,19,FThe Home Office says police use of     
OL,20,Fcameras must be lawful and justified.  
